within which the emphasis is placed on structural factors, functions or types of activity

03:19.000 --> 03:21.000
necessary to achieve the goal.

03:21.000 --> 03:25.000
As tasks are determined and their subsequent grouping,

03:25.000 --> 03:29.000
workplaces, departments and other units are formed

03:29.000 --> 03:34.000
for the purpose of effective specialization and coordination of activities

03:34.000 --> 03:37.000
within the framework of a physically normal workload of the leaders.

03:37.000 --> 03:40.000
Then a coordination system is formed

03:40.000 --> 03:45.000
by establishing the subordination of workers and the boundaries of their responsibility

